      <h3>The Constant Board: From MÃÂ©grine to Manhattan</h3>
      <p>A personal journey through the coffee houses of Tunisia and across the Atlantic&mdash;how a vinyl board, a humbling defeat, and a father's quiet faith in his son shaped a lifelong relationship with chess.</p>
